\fBGL_PIXEL_UNPACK_BUFFER_BINDING\fR
.PP

\fBglGetTexLevelParameter\fR()
with arguments
\fBGL_TEXTURE_INTERNAL_FORMAT\fR
and
\fBGL_TEXTURE_COMPRESSED_IMAGE_SIZE\fR
